<br>
You will also see the difference between the levels because of the penalty that is applied. It is one of the most usefull AA's that clerics get, add to it Cel regen that combo owns. <br>
<br>
If you are in a group with a Pali have them keep up their group heal it is a great way to help their own aggro. You pop DArb and they Group heal you get no aggro from the AA and the Pali gets all the healing aggro <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  When with a Pali I use it everytime it pops.<br>
