<br>
Ladani its also a nice ability to have for the instant heal that it gives, or when you're low on mana and need to do something fast.  If I miss that moment where CH will go off reliably in time to save my tank, I tend to use DvA in that time.  Mostly this is with exp pick up groups though.<br>
